goken9cc (0.3.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian packaging.
  * Ships the goken9cc Plan 9 / kencc-derived toolchain (compilers,
    assemblers, linkers, mk, rc) under /usr/lib/goken9cc.
  * Builds with ROOTDIR=/usr/lib/goken9cc so the install prefix is
    baked into the binaries; avoids exporting GOROOT at runtime since
    that variable is also used by the Go toolchain.
  * Installs /etc/profile.d/goken9cc.sh which only extends PATH with
    the host architecture's bin directory.

 -- Rafael Diniz <rafael.1.diniz@nokia.com>  Thu, 21 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000
